    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, ideal for someone looking for a project or a source for parts. The exterior has significant body damage, including several large dents and noticeable rust patches, while the paint has faded considerably. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the engine requires immediate mechanical attention to be fully roadworthy. Expect a car that needs a lot of work but offers a low entry price for the right buyer.",
