    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts exactly as it should, making for a reliable and comfortable driving experience. While the exterior looks great overall, there are some minor stone chips on the hood and very light wear on the driver's seat bolster consistent with its age. All electronics are fully functional, and the service history is up to date, making this a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned car.",
