    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic, well-maintained vehicle! It's in great shape and has been clearly cared for, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience you can count on. While it shows a few signs of careful previous use, it remains a high-quality choice that's ready for many more miles of adventure. Come see for yourself how solid this ride feels!",
      "price": 34500.0,
