      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, meticulously preserved to maintain its original showroom integrity. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior profile and an interior indistinguishable from new. Engineering and aesthetics converge in this singular opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 43500.0,
